result.title: Suzume
result.author: CoMix Wave Films, Story, Lawson Entertainment, East Japan Marketing & Communications, voque ting, Kadokawa, Aniplex, TOHO, East Japan Marketing & Communications Inc., Toho Company, Ltd., Lawson HMV Entertainment, STORY inc., Kadokawa Pictures
result.description: Suzume, 17, lost her mother as a little girl. On her way to school, she meets a mysterious young man. But her curiosity unleashes a calamity that endangers the entire population of Japan, and so Suzume embarks on a journey to set things right.
